      • Vegetable

        public Vegetable​(java.lang.String n,
                 double tn,
                 int wn,
                 int wm,
                 int fn,
                 int fm,
                 double hc,
                 double sc,
                 double bp,
                 int min,
                 int max)
        A constructor for objects of Vegetable class; calls the Constructor of the the Seed class

        This class has two additional class variables namely productsMin and productsMax. productsMin refers to the minimum amount an object of this class can generate. productsMax refers to the maximum amount an object of this class can generate.

        Parameters:
        n - a String referring to the name of the seed
        tn - a double value referring to the time needed of the seed to grow, in mintues
        wn - an integer value referring to the amount of water needed for a plant to grow
        wm - an integer value referring to the maximum amount of water a plant can receive for bonus computation
        fn - an integer value referring to the amount of fertilzier needed for a plant to grow
        fm - an integer value referring to the maximum amount of fertilizer a plant can receive for bonus computation
        hc - a double value referring to the harvest cost of the seed
        sc - a double value referring to the cost of buying a seed
        bp - a double value referring to the base selling price of a
        min - a double value referring to the minimum amount of products a seed can produce
        max - a double value referring to the maximum amount of products a seed can produce
        See Also:
        Seed, FruitTree, Flower
